      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NO I'M NOT (6) was a course and distance winner two back then got way too far back over a mile latest and came home late into third. Back in trip and looks tough to stop. GALAXY GENERAL (3) turned in a good effort last time when not far from the winner. Close to a win and gets chance. ANECDOTAL (1) showed good early dash and led for much of the way before weakening out of it when 4.5 lengths away in fourth over 1300m at this track. Speedy type sure to take catching. COLLISON (8) is usually thereabouts but finds it hard to win, with just three wins from 35 starts. Placed to advantage and can feature in the finish. STRAYA PRIDE (5) is drawn for a good run and must be included.",
